column1: #Text=Baatar Jr. says : " All right , everybody , let 's test the power core .
#Text=" Zhu Li says : " There 's a problem with the condenser .
#Text=" Baatar Jr. says : " Shut it down .
#Text=" Zhu Li says : " I ca n't .
#Text=" Baatar Jr. says : " Everyone get out !
#Text=" Zhu Li says : " Come on , Baatar !
#Text=" Baatar Jr. says : " This channeling ring was cracked .
#Text=That 's what caused the reaction to overload .
#Text=Now we 're taking this whole thing apart tonight and checking everything !
#Text=This has to be ready by tomorrow .
